one_reviews_text: this is one of the most fun games I have. it has multiple modes to keep it interesting, its really engaging and exciting. I love the animated characters and the music :)

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KgtELxcsb8k

From the creators of the amazing 'Cosmic Trip' This new VR game reminded me of the classic game 'Crazy Taxi' but in space and in a VR universe.
And in VR it's very challenging.
